# US-1012 T1T5 Regression Test Set

As a product owner
I want that for the 10 most important use cases T1T5 Test Cases are defined
in order to have a set on regression tests.

# ACC

 - A list of the 10 most important use cases is defined and agreed upon by the Product Owner and development team.
 - For each of the 10 use cases, T1–T5 test cases are created.
 - Each test case includes:
	- preconditions
	- test steps
	- expected results
 - The resulting test set can be used for regression testing of critical functionality.
 - All test cases are documented in the agreed test management tool (e.g. Testiny).
 - The test cases are reviewed and approved by the team.